	(83,'widget_text','a:2:{i:2;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:5:\"About\";s:4:\"text\";s:616:\"Hi, I\'m Rachelle. I am an aspiring web developer, because of that I am always looking for new things to learn about programming and web development. I want to gather as much related resources/ knowledge as possible and hoping that with that and practice, I can gain skills.\r\nI\'m also interested in blogging but I don\'t really have anything to tackle about. I thought that what I was learning is a good topic to start with. But I\'ll be posting other stuff that has relevance to me as well.\r\nSo, I\'m learning things and open for new ideas and comments. Its always good to know someone is reading what I\'m writing here.\";s:6:\"filter\";b:1;}s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;}','yes'),
