	(1,1,'2014-01-31 07:10:30','2014-01-31 07:10:30','Test post','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2014-01-31 07:15:10','2014-01-31 07:15:10','',0,'http://localhost/blog/?p=1',0,'post','',2),
	(2,1,'2014-01-31 07:10:30','2014-01-31 07:10:30','<blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Make it worth it. -Rachelle S.</em></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I was introduced to web development by my <a href=\"http://giolliano.com\">partner</a>Â  last October 2013, I haven\'t really thought of seriously getting into it by that time. I was just enjoying how amazing it is (for beginners such as myself) to make a web page. For a complete noob like me it feels great to finish one. Then I just wanna know more and before i know it i was addicted to it. I do not want to sleep at all. Sadly I had to stop because I have other responsibilities and i have not consider web development as a career.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I can see that it has many opportunities and I enjoy it as much as I enjoy designing ads so I decided that I am going to learn this deeper. And with 3 yearsÂ  advertising background in college, I decided that I need to be a front end web developer, as where I want to excel.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I am making my time, energy and efforts worth it. I will let hard work, natural talent and never giving up spirit take care of my portfolio. I\'m really hoping to get good and apply the skills I am acquiring to my future projects.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">My name is<strong> Rachelle Ann Salvadora</strong>. So what is <strong>manak</strong> all about? I call Giolliano manok. So, as the female version of him he called me manak. And since it sounds unique I am making it my trademark.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Also I\'m going to be posting about my experiences outside programming/development. I\'m just gonna be sharing stuff here and there about random things or things that matters to me.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Watch out!</p>','About','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2014-05-19 07:23:35','2014-05-19 07:23:35','',0,'http://localhost/blog/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),
