	(33,1,'2014-02-09 01:41:18','2014-02-09 01:41:18','<blockquote><p class=\"size-full wp-image-27\">Aspiring web developer.</p></blockquote><p class=\"size-full wp-image-27\">Yes. I\'m still learning how to code and just beginning to get my hands dirty.</p>','Resume','','inherit','open','open','','22-autosave-v1','','','2014-02-09 01:41:18','2014-02-09 01:41:18','',22,'http://localhost/blog/?p=33',0,'revision','',0),
	(34,1,'2014-02-09 09:28:42','2014-02-09 09:28:42','<p>This is my free page. Meaning, I will post anything in here. If not every, most of what will be posted in here will my opinion, experiences thoughts, reviews, progress, or anything that i just wanna share, elaborate, or summarize or just posts to practice my ability to blog.</p>\r\n<p>You may comment. I would be happy and I will appreciate it very much to know that somebody is reading my posts. But take into consideration that everything in here will be subjective, as it is my blog. I encourage critics, as I am trying to learn</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','BLOG','','publish','open','closed','','learnings','','','2014-05-19 12:33:12','2014-05-19 12:33:12','',0,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/blog/?page_id=34',0,'page','',0),
