	(60,1,'2014-02-10 05:46:22','2014-02-10 05:46:22','<blockquote>Make it worth it. - Rachelle S.</blockquote>\r\nI was introduced to web development by my &lt;a href=\"http://giolliano.com\"&gt;boyfriend&lt;/a&gt; last October 2013, I haven\'t really thought of seriously getting into it by that time. I was just enjoying how amazing it is (for beginners) to make a web page. For a complete noob like me it feels great to finish one. then i wanna know more. and before i know it i was addicted to it. I do not want to sleep at all. The only break i have was sleep. Sadly I had to stop because I have other responsibilities and i have not consider web development as a career.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-02-10 05:46:22','2014-02-10 05:46:22','',2,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=60',0,'revision','',0),
