	(88,1,'2014-02-10 07:54:34','2014-02-10 07:54:34','This is my free page. Meaning, I will post anything in here. If not every, most of what will be posted in here will my opinion, experiences thoughts, reviews, progress, or anything that i just wanna share, elaborate, or summarize or just posts to practice my ability to blog.\r\n\r\nYou may comment. I would be happy and I will appreciate it very much to know that somebody is reading my posts. But take into consideration that everything in here will be subjective, as it is my blog. I encourage critics, as I am trying to learn\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','BLOG','','inherit','open','open','','34-revision-v1','','','2014-02-10 07:54:34','2014-02-10 07:54:34','',34,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=88',0,'revision','',0),
