	(182,1,'2014-07-07 06:28:25','0000-00-00 00:00:00','I havent got any pictures for this problem set because I was too busy thinking about how different it is from Mario. Okay. I didnt expect there will be two different programs in one PSet.\n\nLets start with TO DO\n<blockquote>// TODO\n\n/*\n\n1. Prompt user for amount of change.\n\n2. Always use the largest con possible\n\n3. Keep track of the coins used.\n\n4. print the final amount of coins.\n\n*/</blockquote>\n<strong>1. Prompt user for an amount of change.</strong>\n\nFirst, I may now use math.h :)\n\nLet the use know what he needs to do. Follow the instruction and print \"O hai! How much is owed?\" and get the user input using GetFloat. GetFloat() is the floating point analog of GetInt().\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<pre>\n\n\n</pre>','Time for Change','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-07-07 06:28:25','2014-07-07 06:28:25','',0,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=182',0,'post','',0),
	(183,1,'2014-07-07 05:41:04','0000-00-00 00:00:00','I just finished Harvard\'s cs50. YEHEY! Though I can\'t fully celebrate yet. There\'s still a lot more to learn.','A work in progress','','draft','open','open','','','','','2014-07-07 05:41:04','2014-07-07 05:41:04','',0,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=183',0,'post','',0),
	(184,1,'2014-07-07 15:05:22','2014-07-07 15:05:22','Been four days since I last saw you but it feels like forever. I really wanna cry sometimes but no, I have to be strong because I know that you\'re gonna be sad too. And although this distance is killing me, I\'m kind of thankful about it because it makes me realise everyday of how much I wanted to be with you and its only you that I want to be with.\r\n\r\nI couldn\'t stop crying the day you were leaving even how many times I tell myself that we\'re going to be together again soon, it still hurts so much to know that I\'m not going to be able to hug you again for a few months. I don\'t know but it kind of reminds me how much you mean to me.\r\n\r\nEvery time I see you sleeping in front of the camera, I just can\'t help but wish to be next to you.\r\n\r\nIts so hard to let you go at the airport. To let you turn around and leave even if I really wanted you stay.It breaks my heart to say \"go\". I just couldn\'t help but cry. I didn\'t want to hug you for another second because I\'m afraid I might not be able to take my arms off you. I was pushing you even if I really wanna pull you back and ask you to stay even just for another minute.\r\n\r\nI love you so much.\r\n\r\nI can\'t explain how I\'m feeling right now. But I\'m sure of one thing, I wanna be with you. Only you.\r\n\r\nHonestly, I can\'t sleep. I wanna get on my table and study. I wanna be with you so bad that I don\'t wanna waste any time. I don\'t wanna sleep. I wanna be able to work as soon as possible. I just really want to be with you.','Love, Rachelle.','','publish','open','open','123','love-rachelle','','','2014-07-07 15:05:22','2014-07-07 15:05:22','',0,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=184',0,'post','',0),
	(185,1,'2014-07-07 15:05:22','2014-07-07 15:05:22','Been four days since I last saw you but it feels like forever. I really wanna cry sometimes but no, I have to be strong because I know that you\'re gonna be sad too. And although this distance is killing me, I\'m kind of thankful about it because it makes me realise everyday of how much I wanted to be with you and its only you that I want to be with.\r\n\r\nI couldn\'t stop crying the day you were leaving even how many times I tell myself that we\'re going to be together again soon, it still hurts so much to know that I\'m not going to be able to hug you again for a few months. I don\'t know but it kind of reminds me how much you mean to me.\r\n\r\nEvery time I see you sleeping in front of the camera, I just can\'t help but wish to be next to you.\r\n\r\nIts so hard to let you go at the airport. To let you turn around and leave even if I really wanted you stay.It breaks my heart to say \"go\". I just couldn\'t help but cry. I didn\'t want to hug you for another second because I\'m afraid I might not be able to take my arms off you. I was pushing you even if I really wanna pull you back and ask you to stay even just for another minute.\r\n\r\nI love you so much.\r\n\r\nI can\'t explain how I\'m feeling right now. But I\'m sure of one thing, I wanna be with you. Only you.\r\n\r\nHonestly, I can\'t sleep. I wanna get on my table and study. I wanna be with you so bad that I don\'t wanna waste any time. I don\'t wanna sleep. I wanna be able to work as soon as possible. I just really want to be with you.','Love, Rachelle.','','inherit','open','open','','184-revision-v1','','','2014-07-07 15:05:22','2014-07-07 15:05:22','',184,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=185',0,'revision','',0),
