	(212,1,'2014-07-24 14:17:42','2014-07-24 14:17:42','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://giolliano.com\">Le noob</a>Â just gave me a link a Â few hours ago that really inspired me to do some things I always wanted to do but I just think I\'m not good enough, like writing.\r\n\r\nHere is the link to the website: <a href=\"https://giveit100.com/projects\">https://giveit100.com/projects</a>\r\n\r\nThere\'s so many inspiring stories so I\'m giving myself a try. A practice things that I wanted to do. I\'ll spend an hour of my day everyday to just writing and I\'ll never miss a day.\r\n\r\nThis is day 1 of 100. I\'m not sure what I\'m doing and I\'m worried about the coming days because I\'m really not a writer but that\'s the whole point isn\'t it?\r\n\r\nI might share some stories, write about things I\'ve seen or read or experienced, or anything under the sun. This time I\'m committing myself 100%. I always say I\'d blog about something but I just don\'t know where to start or how to finish it or just get lost in the middle, somewhere.\r\n\r\nI have another project that\'s also in day 1. <a href=\"https://giveit100.com/@user40035959728/bcsdwg\">I\'m going to do a speed typing test for 100 days.</a>Â I wanted to be able to type fast enough to beat the noob. or at least get close. lol. I got 42 wmp (word per minute) today. Let\'s see tomorrow. ;)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','1/100 Just Write','','publish','open','open','','1100-just-write','','','2014-07-24 15:07:38','2014-07-24 15:07:38','',0,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=212',0,'post','',0),
	(213,1,'2014-07-24 14:17:42','2014-07-24 14:17:42','Le <a href=\"http://giolliano.com/\">noob</a>Â just gave me a link a few hours ago. ItsÂ <a href=\"https://giveit100.com/projects\">https://giveit100.com/projects</a>. It is inspiring. There are a lot of people who committed themselves with something and improved. Based on what Giolliano told me, Https://giveit100.com was inspired a girl who wants to learn how to dance so she dedicated 100 days Â to just practice how to dance and she did it. Well, I don\'t really know what I\'m supposed to write or what I am going to write in the next coming days of the 100 days I\'m committed to write but its my way to learn how to commit myself to something 100%. I always say I\'m going to blog about something and then I just dont know how to start it and I just don\'t think I\'m good enough. So, I\'m giving myself a try and I won\'t stop at least until 100 days.\r\n\r\nThis is day 1 of my just write project.I\'ve got 99 days left. I','1/100 Just write','','inherit','open','open','','212-revision-v1','','','2014-07-24 14:17:42','2014-07-24 14:17:42','',212,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=213',0,'revision','',0),
