	(217,1,'2014-07-24 15:11:05','2014-07-24 15:11:05','<a href=\"http://rachellesalvadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Screenshot-2014-07-10-11.00.25.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-195\" alt=\"Screenshot 2014-07-10 11.00.25\" src=\"http://rachellesalvadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Screenshot-2014-07-10-11.00.25.png\" width=\"1066\" height=\"819\" /></a>\n\nOfficia\n\nYES! :)\n\nI\'m out of words. When I saw the certificate, I was just speechless. :)\n\n&nbsp;','Thank you, Harvard.','','inherit','open','open','','194-autosave-v1','','','2014-07-24 15:11:05','2014-07-24 15:11:05','',194,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=217',0,'revision','',0),
	(218,1,'2014-07-24 15:12:00','2014-07-24 15:12:00','<a href=\"http://rachellesalvadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Screenshot-2014-07-10-11.00.25.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-195\" alt=\"Screenshot 2014-07-10 11.00.25\" src=\"http://rachellesalvadora.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Screenshot-2014-07-10-11.00.25.png\" width=\"1066\" height=\"819\" /></a>\r\n\r\nOfficial link from harvard.edu: <a href=\"https://os.dce.harvard.edu/dce-public/certificate/verify/4c12a86a-341c-4d0b-bba4-db6385551aef\">certificate :)</a>\r\n\r\nYES! :)\r\n\r\nI\'m out of words. When I saw the certificate, I was just speechless. :)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Thank you, Harvard.','','inherit','open','open','','194-revision-v1','','','2014-07-24 15:12:00','2014-07-24 15:12:00','',194,'http://rachellesalvadora.com/?p=218',0,'revision','',0),
